Log Files Location
Inside container:

text
# Nginx Logs:
/var/log/nginx/nginx-access.log     # Access logs
/var/log/nginx/nginx-error.log      # Error logs

# PHP-FPM Logs:
/var/log/php/php-fpm.log            # PHP-FPM logs
/var/log/php/php-fpm-error.log      # PHP errors

# Supervisor Logs:
/var/log/supervisor/supervisord.log # Supervisor logs

# Magento Logs:
/var/www/html/magento/var/log              # Magento application logs
/var/www/html/magento/var/log/system.log    # System logs
/var/www/html/magento/var/log/exception.log # Exceptions
/var/www/html/magento/var/logdebug.log     # Debug logs
